, https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/Dimezije-transparentna-14x12.png 14w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f077926 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"f077926\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6620b42 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6620b42\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Velikost na\u0161ega zaboja je: Dol\u017eina: 60, \u0160irina: 40, Vi\u0161ina: 44 cm. Da pa boste la\u017eje na\u010drtovali in najeli pravilno \u0161tevilo box-ov, si lahko pomagate z na\u0161imi splo\u0161nimi smernicami o \u0161tevilu \u0161katel, ki jih obi\u010dajno potrebujete.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7af6cf6 e-grid e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"7af6cf6\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7195426 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7195426\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Omara:<\/strong><\/p><p>3-5 boxov<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b7bfddf elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b7bfddf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>1 soba:<\/strong><\/p><p>5-15 boxov<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8afdaeb elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"8afdaeb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Pisarna:<\/strong><\/p><p>3-5 boxov<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7a712ed elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7a712ed\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Klet:<\/strong><\/p><p>15-25 boxov<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fac4f29 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"fac4f29\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a20898c elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"a20898c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Prednosti Rabimbox skladi\u0161\u010denja na zahtevo<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-acd3440 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"acd3440\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-941581c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"941581c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5><strong>Varnost \u2713<\/strong><\/h5><p>Va\u0161e stvari so shranjene v varovanem skladi\u0161\u010du z 24\/7 nadzorom. Vsak prevzem in dostava je v rokah na\u0161e preverjene ekipe. Tako ste lahko brez skrbi \u2013 va\u0161e stvari so pri nas v varnih rokah.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8985e48 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"8985e48\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ed45e6b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ed45e6b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5><strong>Udobje <\/strong><strong>\u2713<\/strong><\/h5><p>Boxe vam dostavimo, jih napolnite, mi pa poskrbimo za vse ostalo. Od prevzema do shranjevanja in vra\u010dila, ko jih potrebujete nazaj. To je skladi\u0161\u010de na zahtevo, preprosto in brez stresa.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8b33c2f e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"8b33c2f\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ca6f565 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ca6f565\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5><strong>Urejenost in preglednost <\/strong><strong>\u2713<\/strong><\/h5><p>S shranjevanjem pri nas ohranite popoln red doma ali v pisarni. Va\u0161e stvari so sistemati\u010dno ozna\u010dene in pripravljene na hiter dostop. Brez iskanja in zmede, ki jo prinese prenova ali selitev.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8010243 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"8010243\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-003a400 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"003a400\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5><strong>Prvi prevzem in vra\u010dilo brezpla\u010dno <\/strong><strong>\u2713<\/strong><\/h5><p>Prva dostava prazih in prevzem polnih boxov je brezpla\u010den! Napolnite jih, mi jih prevzamemo \u2013 in tako prihranite \u010das, prostor in energijo.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1e2aaeb e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"1e2aaeb\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1426c2e0 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"1426c2e0\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=